'''四河站'''位于[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]][[四川省|四川省]][[成都市|成都市]][[双流区|双流区]]天府大道南段，于2015年7月25日开通使用<ref name="启用">{{cite news | title = 成都地铁1号线南延线开通 33分钟到天府广场 | publisher = 新浪 | date = 2015-07-25 | url = http://sc.sina.com.cn/news/b/2015-07-25/detail-ifxfhxmp9547545.shtml | accessdate = 2015-07-25 | language = zh | archive-date = 2016-11-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161111193524/http://sc.sina.com.cn/news/b/2015-07-25/detail-ifxfhxmp9547545.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。站名得名于老地名“四河村”。在建设过程中的工程名为“华阳站”<ref>{{cite news | title = 成都地铁1号线南延线获国家发改委批复 | publisher = 四川新闻 | date = 2012-08-29 | url = http://scnews.newssc.org/system/2012/08/29/013612851.shtml | accessdate = 2012-08-29 | language = zh | archive-date = 2013-02-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130221024114/http://scnews.newssc.org/system/2012/08/29/013612851.shtml | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。本站是1号线主线与支线间的换乘站。

==车站结构==
本站曾为地下二层[[侧式站台|侧式站台]]车站，长282.7米，标准段宽度37.7米，开挖深度约16米；成都地铁1号线三期工程开通后，本站成为1号线主线和支线的平行换乘[[混合式站台|双岛式站台]]车站<ref name="封顶">{{cite news | title = 成都地铁1号线南延线5站全部封顶 | publisher = 四川在线 | date = 2014-06-12 | url = http://sichuan.scol.com.cn/fffy/content/2014-06/12/content_8082525.htm | accessdate = 2014-06-12 | language = zh | archive-date = 2017-08-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170825102344/http://sichuan.scol.com.cn/fffy/content/2014-06/12/content_8082525.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = 成都地铁1号线三期进入开通筹备倒计时 | publisher = 网易 | date = 2018-01-08 | url = http://sc.news.163.com/18/0108/08/D7K7JMND04268F03.html | accessdate = 2018-01-08 | language = zh | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180108175701/http://sc.news.163.com/18/0108/08/D7K7JMND04268F03.html | archive-date = 2018-01-08 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。
